title: Hoyer Remarks at a "Rally for a Stronger American Future" (Steny H Hoyer)
text: ( Source : Steny H Hoyer) 'I am so pleased to be here. Emily [Holubowich of NDD United ], thank you very, very much for your leadership. Joel Packer, thank you very much for your co-chairing NDD [United] - non-defense discretionary spending -
